<p class="ayah 98-8" id="8" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَزَآؤُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Their reward</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) with</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their Lord -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَنَّـٰتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Gardens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَدْنٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Eternity,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">flow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْتِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">underneath them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the rivers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِدِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will abide</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">therein</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَبَدًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">forever.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top fir